name: Portrait of the Mitherio Queen
description:
The Mitherio Queen is a mythic figure in the world of Atherisiae, she was known to be a powerful magician that led herself to a royal throne.

No one knows is this story is a legend or a real historical event, but the fact that multiple portraits of her has been found led people to believe that she existed far far ago.

This portrait is one that serve as a proof of her existence.
